column5: We're off to a flying start in the 2010 OFC Tourney. Huge update today with four teams bumping their totals... http://www.ofncommunity.com/forums/index.php?showtopic=39529  Still time to sign up! We need a few more people for our next round of team selections. Enter here... http://www.ofncommunity.com/forums/index.php?showtopic=39531   For those of you that have not yet stumbled across the Tournament section, have a look at what you're missing... http://www.ofncommunity.com/forums/index.php?showforum=44
What can I say except ..... GO TEAM 1 !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
